FBIS3-56759 "drsov012_b_94032" FBIS-SOV-94-012 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Poltoranin Says Chernomyrdin Should Resign LD1901140994 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1330 GMT 19 Jan 94 LD1901140994 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Mikhail Poltoranin, deputy for the Russia's Choice bloc, believes that the best way out of the current situation in the top echelons of power, which he described as a deadlock, would be the resignation of Prime Minister Chernomyrdin. He said this while talking to journalists today in the lobby of the lower house of parliament.
